## Project identity

- **Name:** claude-skills (harness-skills) <!-- auto: repo dir name + CLAUDE.md title -->
- **Stack:** Markdown skill documents + Bash hooks + Python 3 utility scripts; GitHub Actions CI (`harness-ci`); no app framework, no DB <!-- auto: file-type scan; no manifest found -->
- **Repo root (relative to this file):** `../../` <!-- auto: this file lives at skills/xia2/ -->

