## Knowledge Bases

Files to read at Step 2b in addition to AGENTS.md/CLAUDE.md/README.md.

- `.claude/rules/*.md` — architecture, guidelines, orchestration, plan-format, wave-parallelism, auto-correct-scope, behavior <!-- auto: glob, 7 files — high -->
- `rules/*.md` (top level) — behavior + governance; `rules/behavior.md` is the declared single source of truth <!-- auto: CLAUDE.md pointer — high -->
- `skills/README.md` — full skill inventory, workflow chains, handoff map <!-- auto: referenced by CLAUDE.md — high -->
- `HARNESS.md` — harness overview <!-- auto: root doc — medium -->
- `docs/solutions/` — solved problems with YAML front-matter
  - **Index:** read `docs/solutions/INDEX.md` first (single read, O(1)); fallback grep keys: `module:`, `tags:`, `affects:`
  - **Critical patterns:** `docs/solutions/critical-patterns.md` — always read regardless of domain
  - **Stale marker:** `confirmed_at` older than 30 days → treat as potentially stale (per CLAUDE.md) <!-- auto: schema in docs/solutions/README.md — high -->

