## Public API Contract Types

For the Quick condition: changes to these break the contract → fail Quick.

- Skill invocation surface — `skills/*/SKILL.md` frontmatter (name/description/trigger); renaming a skill breaks every doc and workflow that chains it <!-- auto: handoff map in skills/README.md — high -->
- Hook registration shape in `settings.json` — consumed by the Claude Code harness itself <!-- auto — high -->
- Template field names (`Lane:`, `Confidence:`, `### Verify`, `### Rollback`) — parsed by hooks and read by the trust-metrics ledger <!-- auto: risk-corroboration.sh greps Lane: — medium -->

